TY  - JOUR
T1  - Within or Without? How Firms Combine Internal and External Labor Markets to Fill Jobs
AU  - Bidwell, Matthew
AU  - Keller, JR
Y1  - 2013/10/23
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2014/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2012.0119
DO  - 10.5465/amj.2012.0119
T2  - Academy of Management Journal
JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 1035
EP  - 1055
